'''二硒化钨'''是分子式為WSe<sub>2</sub>的[[無機化合物|無機化合物]]<ref>{{Holleman&Wiberg}}</ref>，二硒化钨有類似[[二硫化鉬|二硫化鉬]]的六角形結構，每一個[[钨|钨]]原子都和六個[[硒|硒]]共價鍵結，是以三稜鏡的配位方式鍵結，每一個硒則是以角錐狀的組態和三個钨鍵結。钨和硒之間的鍵長為2.526 Å，硒和硒之間的鍵長為3.34 Å<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Schutte | first1 = W.J. | last2 = De Boer | first2 =  J.L. | last3 = Jellinek | first3 = F. | title = Crystal Structures of Tungsten Disulfide and Diselenide | journal = Journal of Solid State Chemistry | year = 1986 | volume = 70 | pages = 207-209 | doi = 10.1016/0022-4596(87)90057-0}}</ref>。各層之間是以[[凡得瓦力|凡得瓦力]]結合，二硒化钨是在第六族金属二硫属化物中非常穩定的[[半導體|半導體]]。

==製備==
將钨的薄片在高壓及高溫（超過800 K）的硒蒸氣中加熱，利用{{link-en|溅射淀积|sputter deposition}}技術可在薄片上形成正確元素比例的六角形結晶<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Pouzet | first1 = J. | last2 = Bernede | first2 = J.C. | last3 = Khellil | first3 = A. | last4 = Essaidi | first4 = H. | last5 = Benhida | first5 = S. | title = Preparation and characterization of tungsten diselenide thin films | journal = Thin Solid Films | year = 1992 | volume = 208 | pages = 252-259 | doi = 10.1016/0040-6090(92)90652-R}}</ref>：

:W  +  2 Se   →   WSe<sub>2</sub>

==用途==
過渡金屬二硫屬化物是[[二極體|二極體]]，可應用在[[太陽能電池|太陽能電池]]的光電轉換設備中WSe<sub>2</sub>的帶隙為1.35 eV，其溫度係數為-4.6E-4 eV/K.<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Upadhyayula | first1 = L.C. | last2 = Loferski | first2 = J.J. | last3 = Wold | first3 = A. | last4 = Giriat | first4 = W. | last5 = Kershaw | first5 = R. | title = Semiconducting Properties of Single Crystals of n- and p-Type Tungsten Diselenide (WSe2) | journal = Journal of Applied Physics | year = 1968 | volume = 39 | pages = 353-358 | doi = 10.1063/1.1655829}}</ref>。  WSe<sub>2</sub>的光電極在酸性和鹼性下都很穩定，因此可以用在[[光電化學電池|光電化學電池]]中<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Gobrecht | first1 = J. | last2 = Gerischer | first2 = H. | last3 = Tributsch | first3 = H. | title = Electrochemical Solar Cell Based on the d-Band Semiconductor Tungsten-Diselenide | journal = Berichte der Bunsengesellschaft für physikalische Chemie | year = 1978 | volume = 82 | issue = 12 | pages = 1331-1335 | doi = 10.1002/bbpc.19780821212}}</ref>。機械剝離的WSe<sub>2</sub> 單分子膜可以用在製造透明的[[光伏效應|光伏設備]]及超薄的[[LED|LED]]<ref>{{cite web | last = Johnson | first = Dexter | title = Tungsten Diselenide Is New 2-D Optoelectronic Wonder Material | url = http://spectrum.ieee.org/nanoclast/semiconductors/optoelectronics/tungsten-diselinide-is-new-2d-optoelectronic-wonder-material | publisher = IEEE Spectrum | date = 11 March 2014 | accessdate = 19 March 2014 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112042030/https://spectrum.ieee.org/nanoclast/semiconductors/optoelectronics/tungsten-diselinide-is-new-2d-optoelectronic-wonder-material/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

{{link-en|過渡金屬二硫屬化物單分子膜|Transition Metal Dichalcogenide monolayers|WSe<sub>2</sub>單分子膜}}因為其性質和一般的二硒化钨不同，也有科學家在進行相關研究。

